* bpfc: Berkeley Packet Filter compiler
  + Generates filter files that can be read by netsniff-ng
  + Own high-level filter language

* tgc: trafgen config file generator
  + Generates full packets, i.e. with support for
    - VLAN
    - MPLS
    - BPDU
    - IGMP
    - DNS
    - ARP
    - ICMP
    - HTTP
    - IPv4 / IPv6
    - UDP / TCP
    - ...
  + Can be interpreted and transmitted by trafgen

